\",\"OL36696129M\",\"OL36345036M\",\"OL36345043M\",\"OL39492768M\",\"OL37844840M\",\"OL37829388M\",\"OL23038810M\",\"OL37389561M\",\"OL35992755M\",\"OL35624257M\",\"OL31983499M\",\"OL36696130M\",\"OL37045177M\",\"OL35723750M\",\"OL34171817M\",\"OL34086917M\",\"OL34081944M\",\"OL34023955M\",\"OL34103282M\",\"OL32038910M\",\"OL32332933M\",\"OL31871274M\",\"OL31834713M\",\"OL31834714M\",\"OL35676065M\",\"OL34791070M\",\"OL26142480M\",\"OL32784488M\",\"OL32222457M\",\"OL32582210M\",\"OL29468910M\",\"OL30167068M\",\"OL30189840M\",\"OL30621390M\",\"OL32050734M\",\"OL32050615M\",\"OL31401961M\",\"OL29882031M\",\"OL30014180M\",\"OL29723715M\",\"OL31445670M\",\"OL30679781M\",\"OL28696529M\",\"OL29496285M\",\"OL30494726M\",\"OL28619596M\",\"OL29260077M\",\"OL29278359M\",\"OL29106843M\",\"OL29259868M\",\"OL30679779M\",\"OL30679780M\",\"OL31191351M\",\"OL30630164M\",\"OL28619595M\",\"OL28425675M\",\"OL28292460M\",\"OL28435584M\",\"OL28132344M\",\"OL27998507M\",\"OL28009102M\",\"OL27974246M\",\"OL27939879M\",\"OL25662679M\",\"OL27697074M\",\"OL27291631M\",\"OL27308141M\",\"OL26378148M\",\"OL27497553M\",\"OL27288776M\",\"OL27096266M\",\"OL27642372M\",\"OL27043019M\",\"OL26939404M\",\"OL27460217M\",\"OL23029279M\",\"OL20569571M\",\"OL23024206M\",\"OL23035226M\",\"OL19680813M\",\"OL23050677M\",\"OL22858290M\",\"OL23038915M\",\"OL23032880M\",\"OL23037597M\",\"OL19679484M\",\"OL23049290M\",\"OL23032819M\",\"OL19220977M\",\"OL23019679M\",\"OL18884467M\",\"OL23018371M\",\"OL23059913M\",\"OL23096517M\",\"OL23017268M\",\"OL23021231M\",\"OL7961781M\",\"OL16786331M\",\"OL13639000M\",\"OL18137709M\",\"OL24329396M\",\"OL9073667M\",\"OL8993476M\",\"OL26418548M\",\"OL23032778M\",\"OL9168345M\",\"OL9894276M\",\"OL26469728M\",\"OL8786537M\",\"OL3688332M\",\"OL18345253M\",\"OL11999814M\",\"OL8786504M\",\"OL26331930M\",\"OL16418942M\",\"OL691894M\",\"OL22620224M\",\"OL9142275M\",\"OL8993490M\",\"OL23097210M\",\"OL26352045M\",\"OL11999828M\",\"OL8993477M\",\"OL22440379M\",\"OL23278082M\",\"OL22595027M\",\"OL8993487M\",\"OL7962603M\",\"OL7962550M\",\"OL7962629M\",\"OL23530831M\",\"OL48544M\",\"OL10735289M\",\"OL23070489M\",\"OL7962157M\",\"OL9831194M\",\"OL11999784M\",\"OL23024436M\",\"OL7961604M\",\"OL22856696M\",\"OL23018382M\",\"OL16180205M\",\"OL22742954M\",\"OL9142328M\",\"OL9044527M\",\"OL9142288M\",\"OL21999413M\",\"OL26336382M\",\"OL9142316M\",\"OL9142298M\",\"OL25726808M\",\"OL12396401M\",\"OL9155292M\",\"OL9641068M\",\"OL13312284M\",\"OL10756444M\",\"OL7962285M\",\"OL9140234M\",\"OL25114262M\",\"OL9064540M\",\"OL9072164M\",\"OL25726807M\",\"OL22723513M\",\"OL9352591M\",\"OL9158008M\",\"OL10457205M\",\"OL24091967M\",\"OL8786539M\",\"OL8993486M\",\"OL11999783M\",\"OL15571091M\",\"OL9155296M\",\"OL9190999M\",\"OL9149800M\",\"OL18633382M\",\"OL7723160M\",\"OL8840179M\",\"OL8840019M\",\"OL9058508M\",\"OL10457203M\",\"OL25726816M\",\"OL9307533M\",\"OL26199270M\",\"OL8171923M\",\"OL25726811M\",\"OL22056715M\",\"OL9064559M\",\"OL9324407M\",\"OL25726767M\",\"OL19112084M\",\"OL26018592M\",\"OL9142340M\",\"OL26410525M\",\"OL27696722M\",\"OL26775548M\",\"OL26820966M\",\"OL27693204M\",\"OL26000517M\",\"OL9891523M\",\"OL27606633M\",\"OL7962488M\",\"OL26872489M\",\"OL9204120M\",\"OL27936637M\",\"OL23108074M\",\"OL7723154M\",\"OL27282614M\",\"OL26869801M\",\"OL9142327M\",\"OL26366926M\",\"OL26872110M\",\"OL26811362M\",\"OL23121614M\",\"OL19314531M\",\"OL25796498M\",\"OL26821542M\",\"OL27506554M\",\"OL8786538M\",\"OL27730868M\",\"OL27561577M\",\"OL26865301M\",\"OL25544380M\",\"OL27319792M\",\"OL26824671M\",\"OL30681024M\",\"OL31970533M\",\"OL31386308M\",\"OL30546665M\",\"OL28055021M\",\"OL27958188M\",\"OL9600209M\",\"OL9659011M\",\"OL9491201M\",\"OL11042435M\",\"OL9898006M\",\"OL26412608M\",\"OL27281088M\",\"OL12856569M\",\"OL26820960M\",\"OL26629979M\",\"OL9064555M\",\"OL26090816M\",\"OL26855047M\",\"OL27209671M\",\"OL26407867M\",\"OL26843077M\",\"OL26855930M\",\"OL9092908M\",\"OL26636884M\",\"OL7723222M\",\"OL8786536M\",\"OL26784380M\",\"OL8171973M\"],\"first_publish_year\":1997,\"first_sentence\":[\"Ο κύριος και η κυρία Ντάρσλι, που έμεναν στον αριθμό 4 της οδού Πριβέτ, έλεγαν συχνά, και πάντα με υπερυφάνεια, πως ήταν απόλυτα φυσιολογικοί άνθρωποι, τίποτε περισσότερο ή λιγότερο.\",\"O Sr. e a Sra. Dursley, da rua dos Alfeneiros, nº 4, se orgulhavam de dizer que eram perfeitamente normais, muito bem, [...]\",\"Bhi conai ar mhuintir Dursley in uimhir a ceathair privet Drive, agus e le maiomh acu go raibh siad an-normalta go deo, agus iad brea sasta de.\",\"Pan ddeffrodd Mr a Mrs Dursley ar y bore Mawrth tamp, llwyd hwnnw lle mae ein stori ni'n dechrau, doedd dim byd yn yr awyr gymylog tu allan i awrymu y byddai pethau rhyfedd ac anesboiadwy'n digwydd dros y wlad i gyd cyn bo hir.\",\"Bhí conai ar mhuintir Dursley in uimhir a ceathair Privet Drive, agus é le smaiomh acu go raibh siad an-normalta go deo, agus iad bréa sasta de.\",\"Mr et Mrs Dursley, qui habitaient au 4, Privet Drive, avaient toujours affirmé avec la plus grande fierté qu’ils étaient parfaitement normaux, merci pour eux. Jamais quiconque n’aurait imaginé qu’ils puissent se trouver impliqués dans quoi que ce soit d’étrange ou de mystérieux. Ils n’avaient pas de temps à perdre avec des sornettes.\",\"Mr and Mrs Dursley, of number four, Privet Drive, were proud to say that they were perfectly normal, thank you very much.\",\"Il signore e la signora Dursley, di Privet Drive numero 4, erano orgogliosi di poter affermare che erano perfettamente normali, e grazie tante. Erano le ultime persone al mondo da cui aspettarsi che avessero a che fare con cose strane o misteriose, perché sciocchezze del genere proprio non le approvavano.\",\"Dominus et Domina Dursley, qui vivebant in aedibus Gestationis Lingustrorum numero quattuor signatis, non sine superbia dicebant se ratione ordinaria vivendi uti neque se paenitere illius rationis.\",\"Mr. and Mrs. Dursley, of number four, Privet Drive, were proud to say they were perfectly normal, thank you very much.\",\"Mr. and Mrs. Dursley, of number four, Privet Drive, were proud to say that they were perfectly normal, thank\\r\\nyou very much.\",\"El señor y la señora Dursley, que vivían en el número 4 de Privet Drive, estaban orgullosos de decir que eran muy normales, afortunadamente.\"],\"key\":\"/works/OL82563W\",\"title\":\"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone\"},{\"author_name\":[\"Trivion Books\"],\"edition_key\":[\"OL37849989M\"],\"first_publish_year\":2016,\"key\":\"/works/OL27731185W\",\"title\":\"Trivia : Station Eleven\"},{\"author_name\":[\"Omni Reads\"],\"edition_key\":[\"OL38975649M\"],\"first_publish_year\":2020,\"key\":\"/works/OL28455020W\",\"title\":\"Summary of Station Eleven\"},{\"author_name\":[\"QuickRead\"],\"edition_key\":[\"OL55855838M\"],\"first_publish_year\":2015,\"key\":\"/works/OL41112711W\",\"title\":\"Station Eleven\"}]}"
